 <title>Mata Atlântica no litoral norte</title>
 <link>http://ubalab.org/blog/mata-atlantica-no-litoral-norte</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;INPE e SOS Mata Atlântica &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sosma.org.br/blog/?p=8605&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;divulgaram semana passada&lt;/a&gt; o estado da preservação da Mata Atlântica. O Imprensa Livre &lt;a href=&quot;http://imprensalivre.com/busca/top_busca.php?edit=3&amp;amp;id=43207&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;noticiou&lt;/a&gt; que Ubatuba continua tendo o maior espaço remanescente.Fui pesquisar um pouco mais sobre isso e acabei encontrando a &lt;a href=&quot;http://mapas.sosma.org.br/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;plataforma georreferenciada&lt;/a&gt; do SOSMA, com dados de preservação (de 2008) no Brasil inteiro.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-1 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/category/tags/mata-atl%C3%A2ntica&quot;&gt;mata atlântica&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/ubatuba&quot;&gt;ubatuba&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/geo&quot;&gt;geo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/ubalab&quot;&gt;ubalab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/inpe&quot;&gt;inpe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/sos-mata-atlantica&quot;&gt;sos mata atlântica&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
